snippet.title: Anode Heart | Steam Trailer (Demo)
snippet.description:
Anode Heart is a semi-open world monster tamer RPG, inspired by the PSX era Digimon World games and monster tamers alike.
+ Wishlist on Steam + https://store.steampowered.com/app/1592750/Anode_Heart/

Demo: https://stoch.itch.io/anode-heart
Support: https://www.patreon.com/anodeheart
Wiki: https://anode-heart.fandom.com/wiki/Anode_Heart_Wiki
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/anodeheart/
